Send Kim in.

30
00:04:36.032 --> 00:04:40.699
Mysterious Fish Deaths
at Jinyang Reservoir

31
00:04:49.282 --> 00:04:50.282
What should we do?

32
00:04:50.866 --> 00:04:52.824
Sell all related funds.

33
00:04:53.157 --> 00:04:55.282
- Everything?
- Yeah.

34
00:04:55.741 --> 00:04:58.074
