35
00:04:58.282 --> 00:05:01.824
Market stability
and individual traders will...

36
00:05:01.866 --> 00:05:04.157
- Kim.
- Sir?

37
00:05:05.116 --> 00:05:07.574
Do you work for the lemmings?

38
00:05:09.491 --> 00:05:11.407
Sell everything. Right away.

39
00:05:12.532 --> 00:05:13.741
Yes. sir.

40
00:05:16.366 --> 00:05:18.032
One minute.

41
00:05:20.282 --> 00:05:23.741
What are kids into these days?

42
00:05:28.949 --> 00:05:32.782
Let's not waste time suing each other.

43
00:05:33.199 --> 00:05:35.824
I don't care what you do with your time.

44
00:05:35.907 --> 00:05:36.949
I'm raising Su-an.

45
00:05:37.657 --> 00:05:39.782
How are you raising her?

46
00:05:39.949 --> 00:05:42.241
Do you even talk to her?

47
00:05:42.991 --> 00:05:46.241
She wants to come here tomorrow by herself!

48
00:05:46.407 --> 00:05:47.491
Did you know that?

49
00:05:47.782 --> 00:05:49.741
Stop this bullshit!

50
00:05:50.366 --> 00:05:52.532
You call yourself a father?

51
00:05:52.574 --> 00:05:54.532
