52
00:05:54.782 --> 00:05:58.157
Then bring her here. She wants to come.

53
00:05:58.866 --> 00:05:59.991
Not tomorrow.

54
00:06:00.324 --> 00:06:02.532
You know it's her birthday tomorrow. right?

55
00:06:03.157 --> 00:06:04.532
Of course!

56
00:06:32.366 --> 00:06:34.699
- Did you eat?
- Kind of.

57
00:06:35.157 --> 00:06:36.407
Where's Su-an?

58
00:06:37.407 --> 00:06:40.699
She's in her room.

59
00:06:42.282 --> 00:06:44.782
I can ride the train by myself.

60
00:06:45.449 --> 00:06:48.991
You can come pick me up at the station!

61
00:06:53.366 --> 00:06:54.699
Mommy. I'm hanging up.

62
00:07:08.782 --> 00:07:10.282
It's okay. you can talk to her.

63
00:07:10.491 --> 00:07:11.991
I hung up.

64
00:07:15.199 --> 00:07:17.741
You told her you wanted to go to Busan?

65
00:07:18.949 --> 00:07:22.574
Sweetie. I have so much work lately.

66
00:07:23.866 --> 00:07:26.032
I'll have more time next week.

67
00:07:26.157 --> 00:07:28.366
Could you wait till then?

68
00:07:36.866 --> 00:07:37.991
Here.

69
00:07:42.366 --> 00:07:45.324
What. thought I forgot? Happy birthday.

70
00:07:46.866 --> 00:07:48.699
Go on. open it.

71
00:08:05.782 --> 00:08:08.699
What. you don't like it?

72
00:08:22.657 --> 00:08:24.991
Children's Day this year.

73
00:08:28.699 --> 00:08:33.741
Is there anything else you want?

74
00:08:35.032 --> 00:08:38.866
Busan. I want to see mommy.

75
00:08:39.366 --> 00:08:40.407
Tomorrow.

76
00:08:40.699 --> 00:08:44.616
I told you. another time. okay?

77
00:08:44.699 --> 00:08:47.116
No. tomorrow.

78
00:08:47.574 --> 00:08:51.491
You always say next time. and lie to me.

79
00:08:52.782 --> 00:08:57.366
I won't waste your time. I can go alone.

80
00:09:04.699 --> 00:09:06.741
Are you busy nowadays?

81
00:09:07.032 --> 00:09:08.991
You know how it is.

82
00:09:09.616 --> 00:09:13.616
So you'll take her to Busan tomorrow?

83
00:09:14.074 --> 00:09:17.074
- Yes.
- That's good.

84
00:09:17.449 --> 00:09:21.032
While you're down there...

85
00:09:21.991 --> 00:09:28.241
have a heart-to-heart talk with your wife.

86
00:09:28.949 --> 00:09:32.991
A marriage shouldn't be abandoned so easily.

87
00:09:34.949 --> 00:09:36.782
For Su-an's sake. too.

88
00:09:36.907 --> 00:09:39.991
Mom. I'll take care of it.

89
00:09:42.741 --> 00:09:45.241
It's a crucial period right now.

90
00:09:46.907 --> 00:09:51.949
Sure. You know best.

91
00:09:53.532 --> 00:09:59.407
She was disappointed
that you weren't at the recital.

92
00:10:00.366 --> 00:10:04.449
It's a crucial period for her. too.

93
00:10:27.907 --> 00:10:34.366
Proudly swept the rain by the cliffs

94
00:10:35.866 --> 00:10:42.574
As it glided through the trees

95
00:10:43.741 --> 00:10:45.491
Still...

96
00:10:46.324 --> 00:10:47.907
It's fine.

97
00:10:49.241 --> 00:10:50.449
Baby. it's okay.

98
00:10:50.491 --> 00:10:52.949
Su-an. go on.

99
00:11:08.282 --> 00:11:11.032
Yeah. mom.

100
00:11:11.491 --> 00:11:12.782
Yeah.

101
00:11:13.366 --> 00:11:15.991
No. with dad.

102
00:11:17.199 --> 00:11:19.366
Okay. bye.

103
00:11:19.449 --> 00:11:22.199
See you soon. Bye.

104
00:11:37.282 --> 00:11:40.907
I saw you sing at the school recital.

105
00:11:41.449 --> 00:11:44.491
When did you see it? You weren't there.

106
00:11:46.074 --> 00:11:50.282
I may look like I'm not there.
but I'm always watching you.

107
00:11:51.657 --> 00:11:54.532
You didn't finish. right?

108
00:11:55.366 --> 00:11:56.407
Right.

109
00:11:57.616 --> 00:12:00.574
Why was that? You should've finished it.

110
00:12:01.532 --> 00:12:05.824
Whatever you do. you must finish what you start...

111
00:12:06.199 --> 00:12:08.366
It's worse than not doing it at...

112
00:12:19.241 --> 00:12:21.699
Jesus...

113
00:12:25.907 --> 00:12:28.074
