117
00:13:07.866 --> 00:13:10.032
Attention. please.

118
00:13:10.157 --> 00:13:16.074
KTX 101 bound for Busan is departing shortly.

119
00:13:17.449 --> 00:13:20.699
- Where is car 4?
- Car 4 is that way.

120
00:13:20.741 --> 00:13:22.324
Thank you.

121
00:13:22.366 --> 00:13:24.449
Attention. please.

122
00:13:24.574 --> 00:13:30.366
KTX 101 bound for Busan is departing shortly.

123
00:13:49.282 --> 00:13:50.949
Hye-young. hey!

124
00:13:51.324 --> 00:13:52.782
Your scarf.

125
00:13:52.824 --> 00:13:53.866
Adjust it. please.

126
00:13:59.907 --> 00:14:03.157
Everyone be quiet and sit down!

127
00:14:03.241 --> 00:14:04.657
Okay!

128
00:14:06.949 --> 00:14:08.866
Look. it's Jin-hee!

129
00:14:11.449 --> 00:14:13.491
Hey. what are you doing here?

130
00:14:13.574 --> 00:14:15.741
I'm your cheerleader.

131
00:14:15.782 --> 00:14:17.532
- Are you serious?
- Didn't you hear?

132
00:14:17.741 --> 00:14:19.699
That's awesome. You got your wish.

133
00:14:20.324 --> 00:14:22.657
- Sit with me.
- Do your best!

134
00:14:23.824 --> 00:14:25.491
Hey. Jin-hee.

135
00:14:27.991 --> 00:14:29.532
What're you listening to?

136
00:14:31.866 --> 00:14:34.282
Go sit somewhere else.

137
00:14:34.366 --> 00:14:35.866
It's not even on.

138
00:14:36.157 --> 00:14:41.491
If I tell you I like you. just say "thank you."

139
00:14:41.532 --> 00:14:42.699
it's your fate.

140
00:14:42.741 --> 00:14:45.699
