146
00:15:03.407 --> 00:15:04.324
Don't want it.

147
00:15:04.491 --> 00:15:06.324
- Take it.
- No way.

148
00:15:07.532 --> 00:15:09.866
Mr. Suh. are you on the train?

149
00:15:10.074 --> 00:15:11.449
Yes. what is it?

150
00:15:11.824 --> 00:15:13.657
We've been getting a lot of calls.

151
00:15:13.824 --> 00:15:16.324
There was a strike at Ansan industrial park.

152
00:15:17.074 --> 00:15:18.449
What?

153
00:15:19.574 --> 00:15:23.949
Prep a situation report for me.

154
00:15:24.032 --> 00:15:25.657
