168
00:17:20.866 --> 00:17:22.157
Excuse me?

169
00:17:24.366 --> 00:17:25.491
Hello?

170
00:17:29.116 --> 00:17:30.449
Sir?

171
00:17:37.366 --> 00:17:40.324
All dead... Everyone...

172
00:17:40.866 --> 00:17:41.907
Sir?

173
00:17:43.074 --> 00:17:44.282
Excuse me?

174
00:17:44.699 --> 00:17:46.824
May I check your ticket?

175
00:17:47.949 --> 00:17:49.116
All dead...

176
00:17:49.741 --> 00:17:52.074
Sir. if you do not have a ticket.

177
00:17:52.282 --> 00:17:55.532
you'll be escorted off at the next station.

178
00:17:56.741 --> 00:17:58.199
Everyone's dead!

179
00:18:00.199 --> 00:18:01.157
Pardon?

180
00:18:02.991 --> 00:18:04.282
All dead...

181
00:18:09.282 --> 00:18:10.699
Hey. kiddo.

182
00:18:10.991 --> 00:18:13.782
If you don't study. you'll end up like him.

183
00:18:14.407 --> 00:18:18.574
Mom said whoever says that is a bad person.

184
00:18:19.699 --> 00:18:22.616
She must've flunked school.

185
00:18:22.657 --> 00:18:27.532
Sir. please come out. We'll move to the back.

186
00:19:03.116 --> 00:19:04.407
Urgent?

187
00:19:05.657 --> 00:19:08.282
Two people are pissing. so it'll take a bit.

188
00:19:08.407 --> 00:19:10.866
There. Use that washroom.

189
00:19:11.032 --> 00:19:11.991
Go on.

190
00:19:15.282 --> 00:19:16.907
This'll take a bit.

191
00:19:17.532 --> 00:19:20.199
Honey. how's it going in there?

192
00:19:21.616 --> 00:19:24.616
Sorry. I'm sorry. No worries.

193
00:19:24.657 --> 00:19:25.824
Take your time.

194
00:19:25.991 --> 00:19:27.532
Go over there.

195
00:19:29.366 --> 00:19:31.657
Take it easy. she's gone.

196
00:19:31.699 --> 00:19:33.116
Relax.

197
00:19:41.907 --> 00:19:44.074
Miss. are you okay?

198
00:19:44.491 --> 00:19:45.241
Miss!

199
00:19:45.366 --> 00:19:46.782
Oh god...

200
00:19:48.032 --> 00:19:50.699
A passenger requiring medical attention in car 11.

201
00:19:50.949 --> 00:19:52.157
Chief?

202
00:20:05.782 --> 00:20:07.241
- Hello?
- Yes. Kim?

203
00:20:07.282 --> 00:20:09.824
It's more serious than we anticipated.

204
00:20:10.032 --> 00:20:12.074
It's not just an overnight Ansan incident.

205
00:20:12.782 --> 00:20:16.449
I don't know what's happening.
but it's not a simple strike.

206
00:20:16.491 --> 00:20:16.782
Military Deployed to Control Riots

207
00:20:16.824 --> 00:20:18.824
They say it's nationwide.

208
00:20:19.157 --> 00:20:20.532
- Is it airborne?
- Hello?

209
00:20:20.574 --> 00:20:23.407
- Is she breathing?
- Yes. she is.

210
00:20:23.824 --> 00:20:25.324
But the seizures are uncontrollable!

211
00:20:26.074 --> 00:20:27.991
Sir. what should we do?

212
00:20:28.074 --> 00:20:30.157
I'll call you back.

213
00:20:38.491 --> 00:20:40.324
Indiscriminate Violence at Riot

214
00:20:40.366 --> 00:20:42.699
Oh no. they'll get hurt.

215
00:20:43.199 --> 00:20:44.449
That's terrible.

216
00:20:44.491 --> 00:20:47.699
People nowadays will riot over anything.

217
00:20:47.866 --> 00:20:50.532
In the old days. they'd be re-educated.

218
00:20:50.616 --> 00:20:52.491
You mustn't say that.

219
00:20:54.157 --> 00:20:55.449
Look. look.

220
00:20:55.657 --> 00:20:58.407
What's up with them?

221
00:20:59.782 --> 00:21:00.574
Miss?

222
00:21:02.782 --> 00:21:03.991
What do I do...

223
00:21:07.282 --> 00:21:10.032
Chief? Where are you?

224
00:21:12.741 --> 00:21:14.491
I don't believe this...

225
00:21:24.157 --> 00:21:25.449
Chief?

226
00:21:40.782 --> 00:21:42.949
Min-ji? Hello?

227
00:22:12.824 --> 00:22:13.657
What is it?

228
00:22:17.449 --> 00:22:18.616
What's happening?

229
00:22:21.199 --> 00:22:22.782
Holy shit!

230
00:22:33.324 --> 00:22:35.991
One moment. please!

231
00:22:59.657 --> 00:23:02.032
Hurry! Everyone run!

232
00:23:05.907 --> 00:23:07.449
Conductor. we have a situation!

233
00:23:07.699 --> 00:23:11.032
Sir. violence broke out in the cabin!

234
00:23:23.449 --> 00:23:25.157
Run!

235
00:23:45.449 --> 00:23:47.532
- Oh my god!
- What the hell?!

236
00:23:58.532 --> 00:23:59.907
Get away! Just go!

237
00:24:06.824 --> 00:24:09.657
Get out of here! Head for the back!

238
00:24:10.032 --> 00:24:11.366
Get up! Hurry!

239
00:24:33.282 --> 00:24:34.574
Daddy!

240
00:25:16.532 --> 00:25:17.907
Baby?

241
00:25:19.032 --> 00:25:21.574
Sang-hwa! So damn loud!

242
00:25:21.657 --> 00:25:23.532
Sorry. the thing is...

243
00:25:23.574 --> 00:25:25.032
Get off me!

244
00:25:36.699 --> 00:25:38.449
You idiot! Go help her!

245
00:25:41.032 --> 00:25:41.949
Hey!

246
00:25:42.032 --> 00:25:42.866
What's with you?!

247
00:25:46.866 --> 00:25:48.616
Are you nuts?

248
00:26:03.324 --> 00:26:04.699
Baby?

249
00:26:04.949 --> 00:26:06.782
Sung-kyung!

250
00:26:07.949 --> 00:26:10.782
You can run. right?

251
00:26:27.366 --> 00:26:29.991
Massive Violence. Increasing Casualties

252
00:26:30.491 --> 00:26:32.282
Get away!

253
00:26:43.657 --> 00:26:44.616
