254
00:26:46.324 --> 00:26:47.616
Shut the door!

255
00:26:48.949 --> 00:26:50.241
Quick!

256
00:26:51.199 --> 00:26:52.366
Shut it!

257
00:26:53.949 --> 00:26:55.074
Shut it now!

258
00:26:56.824 --> 00:26:58.282
Just shut it!

259
00:27:05.741 --> 00:27:07.241
I know him!

260
00:27:20.199 --> 00:27:22.032
Where's the lock?

261
00:27:22.991 --> 00:27:24.866
Buddy! How do I lock this?

262
00:27:27.074 --> 00:27:28.532
Do you hear me?!

263
00:27:32.574 --> 00:27:34.032
Let it go.

264
00:27:34.407 --> 00:27:35.116
What?

265
00:27:38.407 --> 00:27:40.699
