266
00:27:50.741 --> 00:27:52.699
They attacked when they saw us.

267
00:28:12.366 --> 00:28:14.616
What in the...

268
00:28:15.241 --> 00:28:17.116
What are they?

269
00:28:20.741 --> 00:28:22.491
Su-an. you okay?

270
00:28:23.866 --> 00:28:25.282
Hey. buddy.

271
00:28:26.199 --> 00:28:27.574
What is it?

272
00:28:28.824 --> 00:28:30.782
Think you might owe me an apology?

273
00:28:31.116 --> 00:28:32.407
What do you mean?

274
00:28:32.657 --> 00:28:34.032
Look at this chump.

275
00:28:34.574 --> 00:28:37.532
You shut the door in our faces. asshole!

276
00:28:37.616 --> 00:28:40.282
You weren't the only ones in danger!

277
00:28:41.741 --> 00:28:43.282
What a piece of work.

278
00:28:44.032 --> 00:28:44.907
Come over here.

279
00:28:44.991 --> 00:28:46.657
I'll feed you to them.

280
00:28:46.741 --> 00:28:48.116
Stop it!

281
00:28:48.324 --> 00:28:49.949
Everyone's just scared.

282
00:28:54.782 --> 00:28:56.699
Attention. please.

283
00:28:56.824 --> 00:29:02.074
Due to the current situation.
we will no longer be stopping in Cheonan.

284
00:29:02.491 --> 00:29:06.116
For your safety. please remain in your seats.

285
00:29:11.532 --> 00:29:13.616
Hello? Anyone there?

286
00:29:13.657 --> 00:29:15.657
Yes. go ahead.

287
00:29:15.741 --> 00:29:19.574
Do you even know what's going on back here?

288
00:29:19.741 --> 00:29:21.324
Why aren't you stopping in Cheonan?

289
00:29:21.449 --> 00:29:22.782
We are aware. sir.

290
00:29:22.866 --> 00:29:26.366
This is an order from our control center.

291
00:29:26.449 --> 00:29:27.699
Please be seated.

292
00:29:27.782 --> 00:29:32.407
That's nonsense! People are going rabid!

293
00:29:32.824 --> 00:29:35.199
Stop in Cheonan. got it?!

294
00:29:36.532 --> 00:29:38.032
Excuse me.

295
00:29:41.616 --> 00:29:44.407
I'm really sorry. but could she sit down?

296
00:29:44.491 --> 00:29:45.866
She's pregnant.

297
00:29:45.991 --> 00:29:46.824
Okay.

298
00:29:46.991 --> 00:29:47.741
Sit. sit.

299
00:29:47.949 --> 00:29:48.907
Thank you.

300
00:29:48.991 --> 00:29:51.032
Mother

301
00:29:52.824 --> 00:29:53.616
Mom.

302
00:29:53.782 --> 00:29:57.491
Are you on your way?

303
00:29:58.324 --> 00:29:59.991
Yes. we're en route.

304
00:30:00.907 --> 00:30:02.907
Where are you? Why is it so loud?

305
00:30:03.032 --> 00:30:06.907
What's happening? Everyone's fighting.

306
00:30:07.491 --> 00:30:10.991
Are you and Su-an okay?

307
00:30:11.241 --> 00:30:14.241
Why're you breathing like that? Are you hurt?

308
00:30:15.074 --> 00:30:17.657
Seok-woo. my baby.

309
00:30:18.241 --> 00:30:22.949
Please take care of Su-an.

310
00:30:23.116 --> 00:30:24.741
Mom. you okay?

311
00:30:25.782 --> 00:30:28.866
My dear Su-an...

312
00:30:31.782 --> 00:30:37.866
I love her so much. but she only wants her mom...

313
00:30:40.241 --> 00:30:42.449
That bitch!

314
00:30:50.074 --> 00:30:51.449
Mom?

315
00:30:53.699 --> 00:30:54.866
Dad.

316
00:30:57.241 --> 00:30:58.407
Dad!

317
00:31:00.199 --> 00:31:02.449
Is granny okay?

318
00:31:10.032 --> 00:31:13.032
What the hell?

319
00:31:13.741 --> 00:31:15.532
Sweetie. sit down.

320
00:32:00.157 --> 00:32:02.032
My fellow citizens.

321
00:32:02.574 --> 00:32:09.199
Violent riots have broken out in
a number of our major cities.

322
00:32:09.491 --> 00:32:14.199
resulting in multiple civilian
and police injuries.

323
00:32:15.032 --> 00:32:19.282
These riots have led us to shut down
a number of key districts.

324
00:32:19.324 --> 00:32:23.907
in an effort to subdue those attempting to destroy

325
00:32:24.241 --> 00:32:26.991
or take over government property.

326
00:32:28.741 --> 00:32:32.407
For this reason. we're declaring
a state of emergency

327
00:32:32.907 --> 00:32:39.324
in order to stabilize
and control the current situation.

328
00:32:41.699 --> 00:32:47.949
Thanks to our government's rapid response.

329
00:32:48.324 --> 00:32:52.032
a number of outbreaks are being contained.

330
00:32:53.157 --> 00:32:54.824
Fellow citizens.

331
00:32:54.866 --> 00:33:00.532
please refrain from reacting to baseless rumors.

332
00:33:01.074 --> 00:33:06.616
HOT KEYWORD: ZOMBIE
and stay in the safety of your homes.

333
00:33:07.032 --> 00:33:09.907
We must stay calm and trust our government.

334
00:33:10.324 --> 00:33:13.449
as we all work together
in facing this current crisis.

335
00:33:14.574 --> 00:33:18.532
To the best of our knowledge.
your safety is not in jeopardy.

336
00:33:32.032 --> 00:33:35.407
Analyst Kim

337
00:33:40.199 --> 00:33:42.491
Mommy's phone is off.

338
00:33:46.241 --> 00:33:49.199
Those in the front. hurry up!

339
00:33:49.574 --> 00:33:51.282
Su-an. sit over here.

340
00:33:51.866 --> 00:33:54.157
Don't worry. I'll give her a call.

341
00:33:55.991 --> 00:33:57.449
Jong-gil. come sit down.

342
00:33:57.616 --> 00:33:59.824
You're older. You sit down.

343
00:33:59.907 --> 00:34:01.074
I'm fine. Take it.

344
00:34:01.157 --> 00:34:02.991
Baby. let's go over there.

345
00:34:07.741 --> 00:34:10.032
Ma'am. please take my seat.

346
00:34:10.074 --> 00:34:13.199
- I'm okay.
- No. please sit.

347
00:34:17.366 --> 00:34:18.282
Child.

348
00:34:19.116 --> 00:34:20.491
Would you like one?

349
00:34:23.032 --> 00:34:24.824
Thank you.

350
00:34:24.866 --> 00:34:26.616
What a great kid.

351
00:34:31.241 --> 00:34:33.866
- We both got seats.
- Keep walking.

352
00:34:34.657 --> 00:34:36.116
That bag...

353
00:34:37.407 --> 00:34:39.824
Su-an. you didn't have to do that.

354
00:34:40.241 --> 00:34:42.907
- Do what?
- Be so good.

355
00:34:43.324 --> 00:34:46.407
At a time like this. only watch out for yourself.

356
00:34:49.366 --> 00:34:50.824
Answer me.

357
00:34:55.532 --> 00:34:59.074
Granny's knees always hurt her.

358
00:35:00.491 --> 00:35:01.991
Sweetie...

359
00:35:06.782 --> 00:35:09.907
May I have your attention. please.

360
00:35:10.282 --> 00:35:14.116
Our train will terminate service
at Daejeon station.

361
00:35:14.532 --> 00:35:19.824
Military is deployed at this location
to secure our train.

362
00:35:20.241 --> 00:35:24.032
so once we arrive. please exit the train.

363
00:35:24.199 --> 00:35:25.741
I repeat.

364
00:35:26.199 --> 00:35:28.657
Daejeon station will be our last stop.

365
00:35:29.116 --> 00:35:30.949
Which cities can be entered?

366
00:35:31.616 --> 00:35:34.366
Yeosu. Uljin. Busan. What about Daejeon?

367
00:35:34.407 --> 00:35:36.032
Excuse me. I need to use it.

368
00:35:36.657 --> 00:35:38.116
What about Daejeon?

369
00:35:38.491 --> 00:35:39.866
Why not?!

370
00:35:41.532 --> 00:35:44.074
Sweetie. stay put.

371
00:35:47.907 --> 00:35:49.324
Hey. kiddo.

372
00:35:49.574 --> 00:35:50.199
Yes?

373
00:35:50.574 --> 00:35:52.324
Who is this? Your dad?

374
00:35:53.282 --> 00:35:53.907
Yes.

375
00:35:54.199 --> 00:35:55.657
- Real dad?
- Yes.

376
00:35:56.907 --> 00:35:58.282
I wanna know.

377
00:35:59.074 --> 00:36:00.282
What does he do?

378
00:36:00.532 --> 00:36:02.657
He's a fund manager.

379
00:36:02.741 --> 00:36:05.074
- Fund manager?
- Yes.

380
00:36:05.824 --> 00:36:07.907
So he's a bloodsucker.

381
00:36:08.491 --> 00:36:10.324
He leeches off others.

382
00:36:10.407 --> 00:36:13.616
Don't say that in front of his child.

383
00:36:13.699 --> 00:36:14.907
It's okay.

384
00:36:15.032 --> 00:36:18.407
It's what everyone's thinking.

385
00:36:24.241 --> 00:36:25.657
Want some?

386
00:36:26.574 --> 00:36:28.616
It's what Sleepy eats.

387
00:36:29.782 --> 00:36:32.491
This is Sleepy. Say hello.

388
00:36:33.616 --> 00:36:36.074
Baby's name is Sleepy?

389
00:36:36.324 --> 00:36:37.532
No. the fetus' name.

390
00:36:37.616 --> 00:36:39.782
It's like a nickname.

391
00:36:39.866 --> 00:36:44.366
Her dad's too lazy to come up with a name yet.

392
00:36:46.366 --> 00:36:47.449
Touch her belly.

393
00:36:47.824 --> 00:36:49.116
Right here.

394
00:36:50.324 --> 00:36:51.532
Go on.

395
00:36:56.991 --> 00:36:57.991
Feel that?

396
00:36:59.574 --> 00:37:01.657
I made that.

397
00:37:05.032 --> 00:37:07.491
- You idiot...
- But it's true. No?

398
00:37:08.782 --> 00:37:10.366
Lemmings

399
00:37:12.282 --> 00:37:13.866
Daejeon Lt. Min

400
00:37:20.407 --> 00:37:23.532
Mr. Suh. you've called me at a bad time.

401
00:37:23.574 --> 00:37:24.782
Wait. wait!

402
00:37:24.866 --> 00:37:26.824
Let me ask you something.

403
00:37:26.866 --> 00:37:28.032
What?

404
00:37:29.157 --> 00:37:30.907
I'm on KTX to Daejeon.

405
00:37:30.949 --> 00:37:34.907
KTX? Right this minute?

406
00:37:35.074 --> 00:37:36.782
Yes. I'm almost there.

407
00:37:37.532 --> 00:37:40.782
Is it true military is deployed in Daejeon?

408
00:37:41.407 --> 00:37:43.782
Yes. that's correct.

409
00:37:44.032 --> 00:37:48.157
Is that so? It must be safe there.

410
00:37:49.741 --> 00:37:51.866
Well... it's...

411
00:37:53.657 --> 00:37:57.199
Min. It is safe. right?

412
00:37:57.532 --> 00:38:02.449
Once you arrive. you'll be quarantined.

413
00:38:02.657 --> 00:38:03.866
What?

414
00:38:07.324 --> 00:38:09.657
I'm with my daughter.

415
00:38:10.699 --> 00:38:14.241
Can you help us?

416
00:38:15.866 --> 00:38:16.782
The thing is...

417
00:38:16.824 --> 00:38:20.699
I'll get you a real scoop. Do me this favor.

418
00:38:22.491 --> 00:38:26.532
Don't go to the Main square. Come to the East one.

419
00:38:26.574 --> 00:38:28.366
I'll let my men know.

420
00:38:28.657 --> 00:38:32.074
Okay. thank you. Thank you so much.

421
00:38:39.366 --> 00:38:41.866
All dead...

422
00:38:57.532 --> 00:38:59.241
What's going on?

423
00:38:59.532 --> 00:39:00.366
So quiet...

424
00:39:00.491 --> 00:39:01.532
Is it Daejeon?

425
00:39:09.116 --> 00:39:10.116
There's nobody.

426
00:39:10.949 --> 00:39:12.657
Why isn't anyone here?

427
00:39:30.074 --> 00:39:31.824
Out of my way.

428
00:40:21.699 --> 00:40:23.699
What's going on back there?

429
00:40:26.574 --> 00:40:30.074
This is the violent incident I told you about.

430
00:40:30.199 --> 00:40:31.241
Conductor!

431
00:40:31.324 --> 00:40:32.824
- You're the conductor?
- Yes.

432
00:40:33.991 --> 00:40:35.032
How many can fit in the engine car?

433
00:40:35.616 --> 00:40:37.866
We have to uncouple it and go to Busan.

434
00:40:37.949 --> 00:40:38.991
- Uncouple?
- Yes!

435
00:40:39.074 --> 00:40:40.824
- We can't!
- Why not?!

436
00:40:40.907 --> 00:40:42.532
It can't be done here.

437
00:40:43.866 --> 00:40:46.199
Then where's the military?

438
00:40:46.282 --> 00:40:47.241
Right...

439
00:40:47.491 --> 00:40:49.491
I only just received a report on that...

440
00:40:49.532 --> 00:40:51.699
Where's my business card...

441
00:40:52.282 --> 00:40:55.157
I'm COO of Stallion Express.

442
00:40:55.449 --> 00:40:57.616
All routes into Daejeon are cut off.

443
00:40:57.699 --> 00:40:59.366
All buses were rerouted.

444
00:40:59.449 --> 00:41:00.616
But what for?

445
00:41:00.657 --> 00:41:02.991
The city's been quarantined!

446
00:41:03.366 --> 00:41:05.116
They probably won't let us in.

447
00:41:05.366 --> 00:41:09.741
But Busan is still open! Let's go there!

448
00:41:09.824 --> 00:41:12.241
Wait. if that's true...

449
00:41:12.407 --> 00:41:15.157
- We have to take the others.
- Take who?

450
00:41:15.741 --> 00:41:17.366
Let's check the station first.

451
00:41:17.574 --> 00:41:18.866
Hey!

452
00:41:21.574 --> 00:41:22.824
Dammit!

453
00:41:44.949 --> 00:41:47.741
Restricted Area

454
00:42:05.449 --> 00:42:07.116
Don't mind them.

455
00:42:13.157 --> 00:42:14.116
Come on. sweetie.

456
00:42:14.157 --> 00:42:15.324
Where are we going?

457
00:42:16.532 --> 00:42:17.907
We're going this way.

458
00:42:18.074 --> 00:42:21.282
- Just us?
- Yes. Let's go.

459
00:42:27.116 --> 00:42:28.532
What is it?

460
00:42:30.449 --> 00:42:31.824
I'm going this way. too.

461
00:42:32.491 --> 00:42:35.324
Main square is that way. just follow the others.

462
00:42:35.407 --> 00:42:37.241
I think I'll be going with you.

463
00:42:38.199 --> 00:42:40.032
I heard your call.

464
00:42:40.407 --> 00:42:42.699
About pulling you two out.

465
00:42:44.449 --> 00:42:46.699
I know the others go in quarantine.

466
00:42:48.407 --> 00:42:50.199
It's not true. Su-an.

467
00:42:50.324 --> 00:42:51.782
I'll go tell the others.

468
00:42:51.907 --> 00:42:55.491
- You don't have to.
- Of course I do!

469
00:42:55.616 --> 00:42:58.199
Forget them! We're on our own!

470
00:42:59.657 --> 00:43:03.574
You only care about yourself.

471
00:43:05.782 --> 00:43:09.782
That's why mommy left.

472
00:43:28.616 --> 00:43:29.824
Sweetie...

473
00:43:33.699 --> 00:43:35.907
Here! Over here!

474
00:43:36.032 --> 00:43:38.032
Please help!

475
00:43:38.074 --> 00:43:40.449
Sweetie. stay right here.

476
00:44:00.449 --> 00:44:02.116
Goddammit!

477
00:44:04.157 --> 00:44:05.324
Hold on!

478
00:44:16.824 --> 00:44:18.407
Go back up! Go! Go!

479
00:44:36.657 --> 00:44:37.282
Lt. Min!

480
00:44:37.324 --> 00:44:38.782
- Mr. Suh!
- I'm in Daejeon.

481
00:44:38.824 --> 00:44:41.324
Is everything okay there? I can't contact my men!

482
00:44:41.532 --> 00:44:42.532
What?

483
00:44:42.949 --> 00:44:43.699
Hello?

484
00:44:43.782 --> 00:44:45.449
Help me...

485
00:44:48.199 --> 00:44:49.032
Please...

486
00:45:20.199 --> 00:45:21.282
Come on. hurry!

487
00:45:27.116 --> 00:45:28.074
Come on! Hurry!

488
00:45:41.574 --> 00:45:43.157
Hurry up! Quick!

489
00:45:44.491 --> 00:45:45.699
Take this!

490
00:46:03.782 --> 00:46:05.199
Run! Come on!

491
00:46:10.491 --> 00:46:11.741
Asshole! Come on!

492
00:46:19.907 --> 00:46:21.157
Faster!

493
00:46:23.532 --> 00:46:24.741
Hold them off!

494
00:46:58.074 --> 00:47:02.157
- Over here! Run!
- This way! Hurry!

495
00:47:02.699 --> 00:47:03.699
Here!

496
00:47:07.282 --> 00:47:08.741
This way!

497
00:47:09.366 --> 00:47:10.907
Come on!

498
00:47:10.991 --> 00:47:12.032
Hurry!

499
00:47:12.116 --> 00:47:14.616
Why aren't we leaving yet?!

500
00:47:14.949 --> 00:47:16.615
There are still more people!

501
00:47:16.616 --> 00:47:17.824
Hurry up!

502
00:47:18.074 --> 00:47:20.491
Come this way!

503
00:47:21.824 --> 00:47:23.157
Hurry!

504
00:47:23.491 --> 00:47:24.699
Faster! Here!

505
00:47:38.074 --> 00:47:39.449
Granny!

506
00:47:39.532 --> 00:47:41.449
Please get up!

507
00:47:50.241 --> 00:47:51.907
No. stop!

508
00:47:52.616 --> 00:47:54.991
My sister!

509
00:48:01.407 --> 00:48:03.741
Hop on!

510
00:48:23.532 --> 00:48:24.699
Me too!

511
00:48:25.032 --> 00:48:27.199
Let me in!

512
00:48:27.532 --> 00:48:28.741
Please!

513
00:48:46.907 --> 00:48:49.199
How much longer? We've got to go!

514
00:48:49.324 --> 00:48:50.699
No! My friends aren't here yet!

515
00:48:52.616 --> 00:48:54.866
Those on board must survive!

516
00:48:55.074 --> 00:48:56.199
Ain't that right?

517
00:49:02.907 --> 00:49:04.241
Conductor.

518
00:49:04.907 --> 00:49:07.407
Please... depart.

519
00:49:28.574 --> 00:49:29.907
Run! Let's go!

520
00:49:45.991 --> 00:49:46.949
Look. the train!

521
00:49:46.991 --> 00:49:47.949
Run faster!

522
00:50:07.366 --> 00:50:09.116
Snap out of it. idiot!

523
00:50:38.199 --> 00:50:39.699
Watch out!

524
00:51:00.616 --> 00:51:05.241
Control. 101 could not dock
at Daejeon due to outbreak.

525
00:51:05.449 --> 00:51:08.824
Please advise which station
is available for docking. over.

526
00:51:08.866 --> 00:51:13.616
101. due to unstable communications
it is difficult to advise.

527
00:51:13.991 --> 00:51:18.991
Control. is 101 clear to reach Busan? Over.

528
00:51:21.782 --> 00:51:24.741
101. we'll clear your route to Busan.

529
00:51:25.032 --> 00:51:26.616
Control center. out.

530
00:51:27.657 --> 00:51:30.699
Advise when you make contact with Busan.

531
00:51:31.199 --> 00:51:32.824
101. out.

532
00:52:48.074 --> 00:52:50.741
Attention. everyone.

533
00:52:50.949 --> 00:52:56.116
For the safety of those on board.
we won't be making any stops.

534
00:52:56.407 --> 00:52:58.657
We're heading straight for Busan.

535
00:52:59.741 --> 00:53:02.324
Conductor. can you hear me?

536
00:53:02.449 --> 00:53:03.824
Go ahead.

537
00:53:04.282 --> 00:53:05.616
Were you able to contact Busan?

538
00:53:05.782 --> 00:53:08.616
No. Busan's communications are erratic.

539
00:53:09.407 --> 00:53:12.532
Full speed-no matter what!

540
00:53:12.741 --> 00:53:15.241
Or we won't get in. Understand?

541
00:53:22.574 --> 00:53:24.616
Young-guk. where are you?

542
00:53:26.991 --> 00:53:30.032
I thought you were dead!

543
00:53:30.241 --> 00:53:31.949
I'm sorry.

544
00:53:33.824 --> 00:53:35.866
No one else made it!

545
00:53:36.824 --> 00:53:38.241
I'm sorry...

546
00:53:49.366 --> 00:53:51.741
- Baby?
- Mister!

547
00:53:52.699 --> 00:53:55.324
Huh? Why are you answering? Where are you?

548
00:53:55.407 --> 00:53:57.449
We're in the train washroom!

549
00:53:57.532 --> 00:54:00.407
Washroom? Which car?

550
00:54:00.532 --> 00:54:03.199
Well... it's...

551
00:54:03.282 --> 00:54:04.574
Car 13!

552
00:54:04.657 --> 00:54:06.866
- Get your ass over here!
- Baby!

553
00:54:10.407 --> 00:54:12.699
Was that my kid? Is she okay?

554
00:54:12.991 --> 00:54:15.116
Washroom. Car 13.

555
00:54:29.949 --> 00:54:31.574
Gonna pass through?

556
00:54:33.324 --> 00:54:35.574
Let's say you got through and rescued them.

557
00:54:35.657 --> 00:54:37.782
How do you get back?

558
00:54:41.782 --> 00:54:43.574
In Car 15.

559
00:54:44.782 --> 00:54:46.574
people are gathered there.

560
00:54:52.407 --> 00:54:53.991
Car 9

561
00:55:11.491 --> 00:55:13.699
Only four cars away.

562
00:55:15.366 --> 00:55:16.824
I'll lead.

563
00:55:18.199 --> 00:55:19.699
you in the middle.

564
00:55:20.824 --> 00:55:22.324
and you in the back.

565
00:55:25.241 --> 00:55:27.657
Block anyone attacking from the rear.

566
00:55:39.449 --> 00:55:41.907
I heard you're a fund manager.

567
00:55:44.699 --> 00:55:46.699
You're clearly an expert

568
00:55:47.324 --> 00:55:49.782
at leaving useless people behind.

569
00:55:56.366 --> 00:55:58.699
Wait till we exit the tunnel.

570
00:56:12.991 --> 00:56:14.116
Let's go.

571
00:57:25.532 --> 00:57:27.532
Come on!

572
00:57:29.074 --> 00:57:30.407
Let's go!

573
00:57:46.907 --> 00:57:48.157
Move.

574
00:59:23.366 --> 00:59:24.657
Run!

575
00:59:31.157 --> 00:59:32.491
Out of the way.

576
00:59:36.157 --> 00:59:39.866
They stopped once we entered the tunnel. right?

577
00:59:40.824 --> 00:59:42.282
Probably because of darkness.

578
00:59:42.407 --> 00:59:44.782
Yeah. I think so too.

579
00:59:47.282 --> 00:59:49.199
There's even more here.

580
00:59:50.532 --> 00:59:51.824
What do we do now?

581
00:59:53.199 --> 00:59:54.782
There's no way around it.

582
00:59:55.157 --> 00:59:56.324
Let's go.

583
01:00:00.282 --> 01:00:02.657
- What?
- Give me your phone.

584
01:02:06.574 --> 01:02:08.157
Get that out of my face.

585
01:02:10.782 --> 01:02:12.157
Yo. Jerk.

586
01:02:13.074 --> 01:02:16.282
Felt good seeing your kid. thanks to me?

587
01:02:17.032 --> 01:02:19.491
You grateful or what?

588
01:02:19.657 --> 01:02:22.407
Why is your ringtone so tacky?

589
01:02:23.157 --> 01:02:25.616
What's wrong with it?

590
01:02:26.907 --> 01:02:29.324
How do I change it?

591
01:02:30.616 --> 01:02:34.866
Am I funny? You little rat?

592
01:02:35.324 --> 01:02:36.491
How tall are you?

593
01:02:36.782 --> 01:02:38.241
5'9".

594
01:02:38.824 --> 01:02:41.699
6 miles away. at 186mph...

595
01:02:41.782 --> 01:02:43.157
What?

596
01:02:45.907 --> 01:02:49.157
Two minutes.
The upcoming tunnel gives us two minutes.

597
01:02:49.241 --> 01:02:52.282
- Can we do it?
- We gotta.

598
01:02:52.782 --> 01:02:57.032
If we miss this one.
there's another in about two miles...

599
01:02:57.116 --> 01:03:01.241
I bet you never got to play with your daughter.

600
01:03:03.032 --> 01:03:04.907
When she gets older.

601
01:03:06.116 --> 01:03:09.282
she'll understand why you worked so hard.

602
01:03:11.282 --> 01:03:14.657
Dads get all the shit. and no praise.

603
01:03:15.199 --> 01:03:18.074
But it's all about sacrifice. right?

604
01:03:21.074 --> 01:03:24.241
What's with the look? Did I sound cool?

605
01:03:32.907 --> 01:03:34.491
People rescued. Heading over now.

606
01:03:36.074 --> 01:03:37.824
My friend's coming!

607
01:03:39.282 --> 01:03:40.241
What did you say?

608
01:03:40.282 --> 01:03:43.407
My friend from the other car is coming over.

609
01:03:43.491 --> 01:03:45.699
- Who's coming?
- My friend!

610
01:03:45.991 --> 01:03:49.574
He was in Car 9. He rescued some people.

611
01:03:49.824 --> 01:03:50.991
Rescued?

612
01:03:52.574 --> 01:03:57.157
From there to here.
passing through those monsters?

613
01:03:58.282 --> 01:03:59.991
Without no injuries?

614
01:04:01.241 --> 01:04:02.907
You sure they're not infected?

615
01:04:04.032 --> 01:04:06.949
Are you damn sure?!

616
01:04:08.282 --> 01:04:09.991
What do you mean?

617
01:04:10.074 --> 01:04:12.782
Look. look at them.

618
01:04:13.407 --> 01:04:16.407
Right this moment.

619
01:04:16.574 --> 01:04:20.074
no one knows what's happened to their families.

620
01:04:20.741 --> 01:04:25.407
We don't even know
if your damn friends are infected!

621
01:04:25.907 --> 01:04:28.157
But we're letting them in here?!

622
01:04:33.032 --> 01:04:34.741
I don't believe this.

623
01:04:44.241 --> 01:04:45.657
Sir.

624
01:04:47.824 --> 01:04:50.366
please say something.

625
01:04:50.907 --> 01:04:53.074
They'll be here soon.

626
01:04:55.032 --> 01:04:56.741
Sir!

627
01:08:44.282 --> 01:08:45.699
Get over here!

628
01:08:54.824 --> 01:08:55.907
One!

629
01:08:58.199 --> 01:08:59.491
Two!

630
01:09:05.824 --> 01:09:06.949
