633
01:09:36.866 --> 01:09:37.532
Open up!

634
01:09:37.824 --> 01:09:40.616
Hey! Open this door!

635
01:09:41.241 --> 01:09:43.574
Jin-hee!

636
01:09:44.282 --> 01:09:45.449
Open this door!

637
01:10:00.366 --> 01:10:04.032
Open up!

638
01:10:14.324 --> 01:10:16.449
Open it now!

639
01:10:16.657 --> 01:10:17.866
