646
01:11:15.157 --> 01:11:16.491
Come on!

647
01:11:28.491 --> 01:11:29.824
In-gil!

648
01:11:34.657 --> 01:11:35.824
Young-guk!

649
01:11:38.449 --> 01:11:40.032
Stand back!

650
01:11:40.532 --> 01:11:41.699
Young-guk!

651
01:12:16.491 --> 01:12:17.699
Stay away!

652
01:12:24.699 --> 01:12:28.657
Stay back. baby. Please go!

653
01:12:34.866 --> 01:12:36.824
