657
01:12:47.407 --> 01:12:49.741
I'm getting tired. Please go.

658
01:12:53.407 --> 01:12:57.074
Take care of her. okay?

659
01:12:57.824 --> 01:13:01.657
I'll hold them off. Just go!

660
01:13:11.949 --> 01:13:14.866
