669
01:15:49.991 --> 01:15:51.907
He's infected!

670
01:15:52.949 --> 01:15:54.491
He's one of them!

671
01:15:55.407 --> 01:15:56.949
This guy's infected!

672
01:15:57.032 --> 01:15:59.032
His eyes! Look at his eyes!

673
01:15:59.116 --> 01:16:01.699
He'll become one of them!

674
01:16:01.782 --> 01:16:03.074
