682
01:16:58.116 --> 01:16:59.324
Hurry up!

683
01:17:00.157 --> 01:17:01.616
Move!

684
01:17:03.657 --> 01:17:04.949
Go!

685
01:17:05.491 --> 01:17:06.741
Leave us!

686
01:17:07.116 --> 01:17:08.366
Get the hell out!

687
01:17:10.991 --> 01:17:12.116
Now!

688
01:17:14.032 --> 01:17:15.241
Hurry!

689
01:17:18.741 --> 01:17:21.491
It'll be safer for you here.

690
01:17:21.574 --> 01:17:24.782
