692
01:17:27.157 --> 01:17:28.199
But...

693
01:17:28.449 --> 01:17:29.699
Get the hell out!

694
01:17:30.324 --> 01:17:32.324
What are you waiting for!

695
01:17:32.991 --> 01:17:34.366
Okay. let's go.

696
01:17:36.866 --> 01:17:39.741
Get out! Rest of you!

697
01:17:39.949 --> 01:17:41.241
Get out!

698
01:17:41.282 --> 01:17:43.657
Get out of here!

699
01:18:01.449 --> 01:18:02.616
Let's go.

700
01:18:39.991 --> 01:18:41.366
Tie it faster!

701
01:18:42.324 --> 01:18:43.241
More ties! Neckties!

702
01:18:43.282 --> 01:18:46.282
Shut up! I'm working on it!

703
01:19:01.824 --> 01:19:03.241
You idiot.

704
01:19:03.866 --> 01:19:05.324
Good riddance.

705
01:19:06.407 --> 01:19:10.782
Always helping others before yourself.

706
01:19:14.741 --> 01:19:17.199
Why'd you have to do that?

707
01:19:18.324 --> 01:19:20.782
