708
01:19:22.074 --> 01:19:23.741
So stupid...

709
01:19:30.657 --> 01:19:32.157
Shut up! Be quiet!

710
01:19:33.282 --> 01:19:34.616
Stay in your seat!

711
01:19:35.824 --> 01:19:38.324
What a load of shit.

712
01:19:43.116 --> 01:19:45.532
Finish up. Do the other side too.

713
01:19:56.116 --> 01:20:00.407
Thank you for everything.

714
01:20:01.574 --> 01:20:02.616
That woman...

715
01:20:02.699 --> 01:20:04.907
Stop her!

716
01:20:58.241 --> 01:21:00.907
Control. this is Busan-bound 101!

717
01:21:00.949 --> 01:21:03.199
Requesting current situation in Busan. over.

718
01:21:04.699 --> 01:21:05.824
Control?!

719
01:21:06.241 --> 01:21:07.532
Control!

720
01:22:33.699 --> 01:22:35.657
It's your birthday...

721
01:22:40.116 --> 01:22:41.282
Don't worry.

722
01:22:42.074 --> 01:22:44.157
I'll take you to mom. no matter what.

723
01:22:48.032 --> 01:22:50.366
Aren't you scared?

724
01:22:55.949 --> 01:22:57.491
Of course I am.

725
01:22:59.241 --> 01:23:00.824
I'm scared. too.

726
01:23:05.157 --> 01:23:07.407
I was so scared.

727
01:23:08.032 --> 01:23:11.241
I thought I'd never see you again.

728
01:23:13.241 --> 01:23:18.116
I practiced that song just for you.

729
01:23:22.574 --> 01:23:24.657
That's why I couldn't sing.

730
01:23:26.866 --> 01:23:28.824
Because I didn't see you.

731
01:23:36.241 --> 01:23:39.032
Will you stay with me?

732
01:23:53.574 --> 01:23:56.616
Ex-wife

733
01:24:06.491 --> 01:24:12.199
The person you have dialed is unavailable.

734
01:24:21.241 --> 01:24:25.449
Analyst Kim

735
01:24:27.574 --> 01:24:28.782
Yes. Kim.

736
01:24:30.366 --> 01:24:32.074
Have you arrived in Busan?

737
01:24:32.116 --> 01:24:35.199
Not yet. Where are you? Is it okay there?

738
01:24:36.741 --> 01:24:39.324
Busan succeeds in primary defense.

739
01:24:39.657 --> 01:24:42.616
What? You sure?

740
01:24:42.699 --> 01:24:44.449
Where did you get that info?

741
01:24:45.157 --> 01:24:49.657
Sir. this was started at YS Biotech.

742
01:24:51.907 --> 01:24:56.074
The centerpiece of our plan!

743
01:25:00.282 --> 01:25:01.657
Sir!

744
01:25:02.032 --> 01:25:05.574
This has nothing to do with us... right?

745
01:25:06.407 --> 01:25:08.866
We only did what we were told.

746
01:25:09.241 --> 01:25:12.991
Is this my fault?

747
01:25:16.199 --> 01:25:17.407
It's...

748
01:25:18.366 --> 01:25:20.741
It's not your fault.

749
01:25:23.782 --> 01:25:24.907
Thank you...

750
01:25:27.032 --> 01:25:28.407
Kim...

751
01:27:13.241 --> 01:27:15.074
Attention. please.

752
01:27:15.449 --> 01:27:19.407
Due to a track blockage.

753
01:27:19.449 --> 01:27:21.824
we have stopped at East Daegu Station.

754
01:27:22.032 --> 01:27:25.699
We will be waiting for the rescue team.

755
01:27:26.032 --> 01:27:30.324
or disembarking for another Train to Busan

756
01:27:31.366 --> 01:27:33.699
When this announcement is concluded.

757
01:27:33.741 --> 01:27:39.199
I will find a working train
and put it on the far left track.

758
01:27:39.241 --> 01:27:39.991
What's going on?

759
01:27:40.032 --> 01:27:42.574
I repeat. far left track.

760
01:27:43.116 --> 01:27:47.907
If you're alive. please transfer safely.

761
01:27:49.866 --> 01:27:51.616
Godspeed.

762
01:28:56.824 --> 01:28:59.074
Will there be a rescue?

763
01:29:01.366 --> 01:29:03.866
I heard Busan is safe.

764
01:29:05.907 --> 01:29:07.616
We have to move now.

765
01:30:02.491 --> 01:30:03.657
Oh. no.

766
01:30:52.532 --> 01:30:53.699
Coast clear?

767
01:30:56.699 --> 01:30:57.907
Yeah.

768
01:31:00.741 --> 01:31:02.032
You go ahead.

769
01:31:26.324 --> 01:31:28.741
Have to find a way across.

770
01:31:51.907 --> 01:31:53.032
What in the...

771
01:32:05.741 --> 01:32:06.782
Over here!

772
01:32:43.907 --> 01:32:44.824
No...

773
01:32:45.116 --> 01:32:46.324
Oh. no...

774
01:32:48.491 --> 01:32:49.699
What now?

775
01:32:50.866 --> 01:32:53.782
We've gotta move. Come on!

776
01:33:00.907 --> 01:33:03.032
Jin-hee. let's go!

777
01:33:18.907 --> 01:33:19.699
Stand back!

778
01:33:33.074 --> 01:33:34.407
Jin-hee!

779
01:33:48.407 --> 01:33:49.824
Jin-hee!

780
01:34:01.199 --> 01:34:02.741
This can't be...

781
01:34:08.782 --> 01:34:10.116
I'm sorry...

782
