Daddy! Wake up!

783
01:34:43.366 --> 01:34:47.407
Daddy! Daddy!

784
01:35:03.074 --> 01:35:05.074
What's going on?

785
01:35:08.699 --> 01:35:11.407
Come on. faster! Faster!

786
01:35:11.574 --> 01:35:12.741
Hurry!

787
01:35:18.116 --> 01:35:20.032
