Sweetie. come here!

790
01:36:26.741 --> 01:36:28.699
Su-an. Su-an!

791
01:36:45.074 --> 01:36:46.699
Mister!

792
01:37:04.616 --> 01:37:05.616
Sweetie!

793
01:37:05.657 --> 01:37:08.074
Su-an. come here!

794
01:37:08.116 --> 01:37:08.949
Mister...

795
01:37:09.032 --> 01:37:11.407
Go! Hurry!

796
01:37:11.741 --> 01:37:13.074
Come on!

797
01:37:13.241 --> 01:37:14.574
Hurry!

798
01:37:36.366 --> 01:37:37.324
Let's go!

799
01:39:00.741 --> 01:39:02.574
Hurry! Hurry!

800
01:39:05.574 --> 01:39:07.157
Daddy!

801
01:41:28.324 --> 01:41:29.532
Mister...

802
01:41:30.991 --> 01:41:32.657
I'm scared.

803
01:41:35.657 --> 01:41:37.407
Take me home.

804
01:41:37.574 --> 01:41:42.616
My mom is waiting for me...

805
01:41:46.574 --> 01:41:48.157
My address is...

806
01:41:48.991 --> 01:41:52.866
Suyoung district. Busan...

807
01:41:56.116 --> 01:41:58.282
Please help me!

808
01:42:01.574 --> 01:42:03.032
You...

809
01:42:04.074 --> 01:42:05.407
You're infected.

810
01:42:11.449 --> 01:42:12.699
No...

811
01:42:14.282 --> 01:42:15.491
No.

812
01:42:16.241 --> 01:42:17.407
No!

813
01:42:18.282 --> 01:42:22.449
I can't be! No!

814
01:42:48.782 --> 01:42:50.074
Daddy!

815
01:43:29.491 --> 01:43:31.491
Daddy!

816
01:44:42.032 --> 01:44:43.741
Daddy!

817
01:44:48.532 --> 01:44:50.074
Su-an. come here.

818
01:44:50.241 --> 01:44:52.449
Sit down. Over there.

819
01:44:52.782 --> 01:44:53.907
Sung-kyung.

820
01:44:55.199 --> 01:44:57.074
Listen to me. Pay attention. now.

821
01:44:57.866 --> 01:45:00.116
This must be the brake.

822
01:45:00.532 --> 01:45:04.782
When it's safe. pull this. Got it?

823
01:45:11.116 --> 01:45:12.324
Sweetie.

824
01:45:14.032 --> 01:45:16.616
Look at me. Su-an. It's okay.

825
01:45:21.199 --> 01:45:22.824
Look at me. sweetie.

826
01:45:23.991 --> 01:45:26.616
Su-an. listen to me.

827
01:45:28.116 --> 01:45:31.824
Stay with her. no matter what. Okay?

828
01:45:34.907 --> 01:45:37.324
It'll be safe in Busan.

829
01:45:37.407 --> 01:45:38.907
Don't go!

830
01:45:39.741 --> 01:45:42.407
Don't go. it's my fault!

831
01:45:43.282 --> 01:45:45.366
Daddy. don't go...

832
01:45:45.574 --> 01:45:47.324
Don't go...

833
01:45:48.532 --> 01:45:50.157
Please...

834
01:45:52.157 --> 01:45:53.824
Don't...

835
01:45:55.366 --> 01:45:59.907
